<TITLE> BNP policy forum meets Thurs evening </TITLE>
<TEXT>
 Dhaka, Feb 25 (bdnews24.com)  BNP chairperson Khaleda Zia has convened an emergency meeting of the main opposition party's highest policy-making forum, the national standing committee, at her Gulshan office on Thursday evening, a party official said. Party office secretary Rizvi Ahmed told bdnews24.com on Thursday: "The present political situation and party's organisational affairs are on agenda of the meeting to be held at 7pm." Thursday's one will be the second meeting of the 19-member committee since its reconstitution in December last year
